For women this is usually changed to 8 hours with two smaller meals.]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>In reply to <a href="https://jamesclear.vercel.app/good-bad-intermittent-fasting#comment-4121">Cindy Lee Bergersen</a>.</p>
<p>Changing the eating window is typically what women do to make it better for them health-wise. Typically, for men, it&#8217;s eat all your calories in a 4-hour window with one big meal during the day. </p>
<p>For women this is usually changed to 8 hours with two smaller meals.</p>
