		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://jamesclear-com.uar9g7bv-liquidwebsites.com/?p=5305#comment-10796</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[For me IF was the way to go for many years in my life without doing it based on any protocol. I was always used to skip breakfast drinking a coffee and eating my lunch in that way I was felling more productive during the morning and energized. I still gained a lot of weight the last 2 by eating and drinking a lot around 45kgs. this year I decided to change so I started working out with heavy weights and counting my macro intake. I lost a huge amount of weight but my progress stalled around the 13% I was advised and trying to stick with the general belief of 6 meals -- 5 meals but it doest working for me I was feeling very hungry and exhausted. After some thought I jumped back on IF it helped me control craving and I work out fasted in the morning and doing carb cycling I reached 10% body fat (Leangains protocol) and I feel more energetic than ever also IF helped me with bloating and other gastro problems I had! As it is said, everyone seems to be different so you have to listen to your body and do whatever feels better for you.]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>For me IF was the way to go for many years in my life without doing it based on any protocol. I was always used to skip breakfast drinking a coffee and eating my lunch in that way I was felling more productive during the morning and energized. I still gained a lot of weight the last 2 by eating and drinking a lot around 45kgs. this year I decided to change so I started working out with heavy weights and counting my macro intake. I lost a huge amount of weight but my progress stalled around the 13% I was advised and trying to stick with the general belief of 6 meals &#8212; 5 meals but it doest working for me I was feeling very hungry and exhausted. After some thought I jumped back on IF it helped me control craving and I work out fasted in the morning and doing carb cycling I reached 10% body fat (Leangains protocol) and I feel more energetic than ever also IF helped me with bloating and other gastro problems I had! As it is said, everyone seems to be different so you have to listen to your body and do whatever feels better for you.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
		
